Description: # PySilence
        
        PySilence is an silence detection tool
        
        ### Install
        ```pip install pysilence```
        
        ### Usage
        ```python
        from pysilence import silence
        
        ranges = silence.detect_silence_ranges(
            audio_data=audio,
            sample_rate=rate,
            min_silence_len=2000,
            step_duration=200,
            silence_threshold=0.1,
            verbose=False,
            progress=False,
        )
        ```
